headline: Goldman Sachs Maintains Neutral on Lennar Corporation (LEN) as Incentives and Demand Uncertainty Cloud 2026 Outlook
summary: We recently published an article titled 10 Best Affordable Housing Stocks to Buy. On January 13, Goldman Sachs raised its price target on Lennar Corporation (NYSE:LEN) to $125 from $120 while maintaining a Neutral rating, citing mixed housing signals toward year-end.
